  "detailed_description": "<h1>Buffet Knight’s skills are put to the test in the Golden Potluck content update!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/95703e5d520aa06196f562e6a2f62201.avif?t=1773321027\" width=1170 height=379 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you hear the sound of shuffling cards, rolling dice, and jingling coins?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buffet Knight’s skills are on the table, his fortune tested in the Golden Potluck content update!</p></p><br><h1>Buffet Knight - Decadent Full Course + Original Soundtrack</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/c1be3fe46f893185e680b6e13b5fbe88.avif?t=1773321027\" width=616 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Buffet Knight - Decadent Full Course + Original Soundtrack Bundle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A full meal combo including a main course of Buffet Knight’s adventure along with a side dish of the original soundtrack!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This bundle contains:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buffet Knight - Decadent Full Course Game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buffet Knight - Decadent Full Course Soundtrack</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Buffet Knight - Decadent Full Course Demo</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/dc359e68f7c07ca3efb02a8e6df3ac96.avif?t=1773321027\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Have a taste of Buffet Knight’s adventure in this demo appetiser, featuring up to the end of the first dungeon. Transfer your progress into the full game!</strong></i></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/bfa06d8074c89c60ea3aa7dee30b4ab2.poster.avif?t=1773321027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/bfa06d8074c89c60ea3aa7dee30b4ab2.webm?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/bfa06d8074c89c60ea3aa7dee30b4ab2.mp4?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Feast-Fueled Adventure Awaits</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Demon Chef has pilfered the finest food in the land, plunging the Gourmet Kingdom into chaos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the heroic Buffet Knight, you must adventure across  vibrant regions, defeat enormous bosses, conquer perilous dungeons, and eat everything in your path to grow stronger and restore balance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buffet Knight - Decadent Full Course blends fast-paced action, exploration, and light puzzle-solving into a compact, satisfying adventure built around a unique “consume to power up” mechanic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/30c7f9cf6637aa17c46b95d521ad7796.poster.avif?t=1773321027\" width=600 height=70 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/30c7f9cf6637aa17c46b95d521ad7796.webm?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eat to Grow Stronger. Your Appetite is Your Greatest Strength.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swallow enemies, projectiles, and objects to gain power and turn the battlefield in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/c0540d79e37bc3dc4ba200e3c3205897.avif?t=1773321027\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aim Your Projectiles and Time Your Abilities</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot what you consume to conquer foes and unlock combat abilities that depend on timing and positioning. Movement is key to survival for Buffet Knight - dodge enemy attacks and triumph in victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/835785a539a2772c265878c061d51b40.poster.avif?t=1773321027\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/835785a539a2772c265878c061d51b40.webm?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/835785a539a2772c265878c061d51b40.mp4?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delectable Dungeons & Puzzles</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think through light puzzles to unlock hidden secrets and overcome environmental challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/f64252c7645269ffe8db65d5982ed4cd.poster.avif?t=1773321027\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/f64252c7645269ffe8db65d5982ed4cd.webm?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/f64252c7645269ffe8db65d5982ed4cd.mp4?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flavorful Boss Battles</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against oversized culinary nightmares that test your reflexes and mastery of your abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/b92728e178ac9f23b233c480cbdacfee.poster.avif?t=1773321027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/b92728e178ac9f23b233c480cbdacfee.webm?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/b92728e178ac9f23b233c480cbdacfee.mp4?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tasteful Abilities & Accessories</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your playstyle with stats, items, and power-ups discovered throughout your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/c13088f0dc9fd2236524820ab6907c10.poster.avif?t=1773321027\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/c13088f0dc9fd2236524820ab6907c10.webm?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/c13088f0dc9fd2236524820ab6907c10.mp4?t=1773321027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings & Hidden Secrets</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices and exploration determine how the feast truly ends. Choose wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Cozy, Satisfying Action Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buffet Knight was made to be approachable but rewarding! Perfect for players who enjoy action-adventure games with personality, charm, and a satisfying progression loop. Whether you’re here to explore strange & exotic lands, battle quirky (and tasty!) monsters , solve satisfyingly chewy puzzles or discover delicious secrets, there’s always something new to sink your teeth into. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Great on Steam Deck</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is optimized for Steam Deck and perfect for a cozy playthrough on the couch. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Highly rated by players with 96% positive reviews on Steam <i>as of Feb 2026</i>. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072480/extras/21052777673455737d8d81aa76203795.webp?t=1773321027\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p>",
